#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We had written and adopted a Code of Conduct since our first public hackfest "
"in Paris in 2014. This code was and is meant as a guide to make our public "
"spaces welcoming and friendly to every sentient being."
msgstr ""
"Vam escriure i adoptar un Codi de Conducta des del nostre primer hackfest "
"públic a París el 2014. Aquest codi era i està pensat com una guia per fer "
"que els nostres espais públics siguin acollidors i amigables per a tothom."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We have since then worked on a [[Social Contract|doc/about/social_contract]] "
"which we proudly present today!"
msgstr ""
"Des de llavors hem treballat en un [[Contracte Social|doc/about/"
"social_contract]] que avui presentem amb orgull!"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"note\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"note\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>This social contract has been replaced in 2024 by the\n"
"<a href=\"https://community.torproject.org/policies/social_contract/\">Tor\n"
"Project Social Contract</a>.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p>Aquest contracte social ha estat substituït l'any 2024 pel\n"
"<a href=\"https://community.torproject.org/policies/social_contract/\">"
"Contracte\n"
"social del Projecte Tor</a>.</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "</div>\n"
msgstr "</div>\n"

